ckasaw Nation who is at least thirty (30) years of ag"}, {"t": "5", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#X/5", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE X, 5", "rp": "X|\u00a75", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|X|5", "x": "The Governor and the Lieutenant Governor must be registered to vote and mus"}, {"t": "6", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#X/6", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE X, 6", "rp": "X|\u00a76", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|X|6", "x": "No person who has been convicted of a felony by a court of competent jurisd"}]}, {"t": "ARTICLE XI PRIVILEGES, DUTIES AND POWERS OF EXECUTIVE DEPARTMENT", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#XI", "et": "container", "sc": " ARTICLE XI", "rp": "XI", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|XI", "c": [{"t": "1", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#XI/1", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE XI, 1", "rp": "XI|\u00a71", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|XI|1", "x": "The Governor shall perform all duties appertaining to the office of Chief E"}, {"t": "2", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#XI/2", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE XI, 2", "rp": "XI|\u00a72", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|XI|2", "x": "The Governor shall have power to establish and appoint committees, members "}, {"t": "3", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#XI/3", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE XI, 3", "rp": "XI|\u00a73", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|XI|3", "x": "The Governor shall have power to veto any decision of the Tribal Legislatur"}, {"t": "4", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#XI/4", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE XI, 4", "rp": "XI|\u00a74", "sp": "library|Chickasaw Nation Constitution|XI|4", "x": "The Governor shall prepare and submit an annual tribal budget to the Tribal"}, {"t": "5", "p": "/us/nsn/chickasaw/legislature/constitution#XI/5", "et": "section", "sc": " ARTICLE XI, 5", "rp": "XI|\u00a